<p>You know, you might have a point there. I guess I kept that last bit from a scrapped idea to pit it against 682 (both SCP's survived the ordeal, 682 escaped and looked the closest it had been to being scared the Foundation had seen it get) but that doesn't really make it less ridiculous. I guess I'll change the last test to &quot;no effect&quot; and maybe add a researcher's note that though other fluids are safe, it still doesn't help much since there's no real replacement for water in everyday life.</p>

